urther west or work for barely livable wages at Penn to keep their homes. Were not asking for charitywere asking for the civic Ivy to fulfill its most basic responsibilities to the city that it calls home.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-199 size-large\" src=\"http://phillyjwj.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Screen-Shot-2019-03-26-at-4.56.19-PM-1024x683.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"467\" />\r\n\r\nCheck out our press coverage here: <a href=\"https://www.thedp.com/article/2019/03/penn-protest-nonprofit-tax-exempt-pilot-funding\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.thedp.com/article/2019/03/penn-protest-nonprofit-tax-exempt-pilot-funding&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1553719731007000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHEuxYTFPIMPx5hNL836H0GzS6wuQ\">Daily Pennsylvanian</a> (and <a href=\"https://www.thedp.com/article/2019/03/gentrification-philadelphia-study-penn-upenn-race-higher-rents\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.thedp.com/article/2019/03/gentrification-philadelphia-study-penn-upenn-race-higher-rents&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1553719731007000&amp;usg=AFQjCNGoVedQ4b2vVMJtV8rqzEpUNwZUjw\">related followup</a>), <a href=\"https://whyy.org/articles/education-activists-call-on-penn-to-pay-fair-share-to-support-city-schools/?fbclid=IwAR206fziweH7nzundri1MSgwBPaXvGuTKRZUC7B930wC6t34mAWbzA_HEAM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://whyy.org/articles/education-activists-call-on-penn-to-pay-fair-share-to-support-city-schools/?fbclid%3DIwAR206fziweH7nzundri1MSgwBPaXvGuTKRZUC7B930wC6t34mAWbzA_HEAM&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1553719731007000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHZrkMSVtbov6HM110JGDZeNIkteQ\">WHYY</a>, <a href=\"https://www.phillytrib.com/news/local_news/education-activists-call-on-penn-to-pay-fair-share-to/article_4c797dd0-57a4-5ba4-ac72-622d5c97f709.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirect