rkplace</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span>\n\n<span data-contrast=\"auto\"></span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Police officers should not be above the law,</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;and should not be able to negotiate conditions that put them above the law.</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Derek Chauvin, the officer who murdered George Floyd, had 18 previous complaints against him  but his</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;local</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;union</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">,</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">the&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast=\"none\">Police Officers Federation of Minneapolis,</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;helped prevent his removal</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:240}\">&nbsp;</span>\n\n<span data-contrast=\"auto\"></span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">I</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">n the past, when a</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;local</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;union</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">gets caught up in criminal activity, theyre trust</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">ee</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">d</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> by national union affiliates to democratize. </span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">How many times does Bob Krolls</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;police</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;union</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;in Minneapolis&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\"></span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">the makers of the&nbsp;</span><span data-contrast=\